This is how to simplify of x and n:
  When x is n, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  When x's length is not n's length, then:
    The answer is 0
  End when
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this x's length times:
    When item i in x is not item diff of diff of x's length and 1 and i in n, then:
      The answer is 0
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is 1
